OL,3,CWhat happened to Haltwhistle
OL,4,Cschoolgirl Holly Newton?
OL,6,FThe murder of schoolgirl Holly Newton
OL,7,Fwas an event which shocked Hexham, the
OL,8,Fquiet Northumberland market town where
OL,9,Fshe went to school.
OL,11,FThe 15-year-old from Haltwhistle was
OL,12,Ffatally stabbed in an alleyway on 27
OL,13,FJanuary 2023. Her family described her
OL,14,Fas a talented dancer who was bubbly,
OL,15,Fbright and popular.
OL,17,FFollowing a trial at Newcastle Crown
OL,18,FCourt, a 17-year-old boy - who cannot
OL,19,Fbe named due to his age - has been
OL,20,Ffound guilty of her murder.
