OL,3,CWhat happened to Haltwhistle
OL,4,Cschoolgirl Holly Newton?
OL,6,FHe was also found guilty of wounding
OL,7,Fwith intent of another youth.
OL,9,FThroughout the trial, the boy had
OL,10,Fadmitted killing Holly but denied a
OL,11,Fcharge of murder.
OL,13,FHe was known to Holly and during the
OL,14,Ftrial, the court was told how she had
OL,15,Fmessaged a friend to say he was
OL,16,F"basically stalking" her.
