OL,3,CWhat happened to Haltwhistle
OL,4,Cschoolgirl Holly Newton?
OL,6,FAfter finishing school on the day she
OL,7,Fdied, Holly went into Hexham with her
OL,8,Ffriends. The prosecution said she was
OL,9,Funaware that the defendant was
OL,10,Ffollowing them at a distance.
OL,12,FAt around 4.45pm, Holly went into a
OL,13,Fpizza shop. The defendant waited at a
OL,14,Fnearby bus stop and asked to speak to
OL,15,Fher.
OL,17,FCCTV footage shown to the court showed
OL,18,FHolly appearing calm as she spoke to
OL,19,Fthe boy before they stepped into an
OL,20,Falleyway.
