OL,3,CWhat happened to Haltwhistle
OL,4,Cschoolgirl Holly Newton?
OL,6,FIn the space of over a minute, he
OL,7,Finflicted 36 knife wounds on Holly -
OL,8,Fstabbing her 12 times, slashing her 19
OL,9,Ftimes and causing her five "defensive"
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,FAnother youth told the court he heard
OL,13,Fscreaming and went into the alleyway
OL,14,Fto help. He also suffered stab wounds
OL,15,Fto his shoulder, arm and thigh which
OL,16,Frequired surgery.
OL,18,FA passer-by managed to restrain the
OL,19,Fdefendant.
