OL,3,CWhat happened to Haltwhistle
OL,4,Cschoolgirl Holly Newton?
OL,6,FThe defendant told police he had
OL,7,Fintended to injure himself, but it
OL,8,F"went too far". In court, he said he
OL,9,Fhad no recollection of stabbing Holly,
OL,10,For the youth who came to her aid.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called and
OL,13,FHolly was taken to Newcastle's Royal
OL,14,FVictoria Infirmary but could not be
OL,15,Fsaved.
